@startuml sequence_mode_switch_flow

participant User
participant CalculatorWindow
participant GUISessionAdapter
participant CalculatorSession

User ->> CalculatorWindow: _on_mode_toggle_clicked()
activate CalculatorWindow

CalculatorWindow -> CalculatorWindow: determine new_mode\n(toggle "normal" ↔ "scientific")

CalculatorWindow -> CalculatorWindow: on_mode_changed(new_mode)

CalculatorWindow ->> GUISessionAdapter: set_mode(new_mode)
activate GUISessionAdapter
GUISessionAdapter ->> CalculatorSession: set_mode(new_mode)
activate CalculatorSession
CalculatorSession -->> GUISessionAdapter: ok
deactivate CalculatorSession
deactivate GUISessionAdapter

note over CalculatorWindow: State reset:\n_selected_op = None\n_pending_binary_op = None

CalculatorWindow ->> GUISessionAdapter: clear_pending_operand()
activate GUISessionAdapter
GUISessionAdapter -> GUISessionAdapter: _pending_operand1 = None
deactivate GUISessionAdapter

CalculatorWindow -> CalculatorWindow: _display_value = "0"
CalculatorWindow -> CalculatorWindow: _result_var.set("")

CalculatorWindow -> CalculatorWindow: update mode_toggle_btn label\n("Scientific" or "Normal")

CalculatorWindow -> CalculatorWindow: update_operation_buttons()

CalculatorWindow ->> GUISessionAdapter: get_operations()
activate GUISessionAdapter
GUISessionAdapter ->> CalculatorSession: get filtered ops list
activate CalculatorSession
CalculatorSession -->> GUISessionAdapter: ops for new_mode
deactivate CalculatorSession
GUISessionAdapter -->> CalculatorWindow: ops list
deactivate GUISessionAdapter

note over CalculatorWindow: Destroy old buttons\nbuild new buttons in 4-column grid

CalculatorWindow -> CalculatorWindow: for each op:\n  create button + _bind_hover()

note over CalculatorWindow: Mode switch complete

deactivate CalculatorWindow

@enduml
